Reviews: Honestly the best fish,shrimp & marlin tacos I've had in a minute! They hook you up with a great portion of seafood for your tacos & their so fat & filling, plus the toppings just fire! Highly recommend & will definitely be back, you will not be disappointed I promise lol

The marlin was tasty. Along with the awesome salsas and various veggie toppings this is literally the best fish taco I have ever had! The shrimp quesadillas were also delicious. Definitely my go to spot when I crave fish tacos.

Summary: There is no relevant information regarding the ambience at Bay Taco Fish.
